smtp - Simple Mail Transport Facility

Syntax:	smtp gateway [hostid]
		Identify "hostid" as a gateway device for mail
	smtp kick
		Force delivery of pending mail
	smtp maxclients [maximum]
		Set to "maximum" the maximum number of outgoing SMTP session
	smtp mode [queue|route]
		Set mode of delivery; default is 'queue'
	smtp timer [seconds]
		Scan the outbound mail queue every "seconds" seconds
	smtp trace [level]
		Display trace level, or set it to "level"

